    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Surfaces SBS's open program data (certified businesses, BIDs, Workforce1 events and jobs, service centers, incentives) and adds apply_for_mwbe_certification \u2014 the net-new write workflow locked today inside the MyCity Business portal.",
